data.title: Great service
data.text: Customer service is exceptional, food is average Taco Bell, but the drive thru takes a three point turn to get in and the homeless population is a deterrent. Feel bad for staff, a never ending battle.

data.title: Taco Bell new location
data.text: Great drive thru... love to get my food fast and these guys do it well! Keep it up always. Great location...

data.title: Nice addition to the chain.
data.text: A few months ago, a new Taco Bell appeared in Antioch. I waited a while to go there because usually when a new place opens up it is crazy-busy due to being new. When I finally went in for lunch, I found great customer service and a building that was well maintained, (trash removed, windows clean including the glass doors and very clean bathrooms). The food was great! and if you've read some of my ratings of this chain, is seldom the case. Kudos to the management and employees for the work they do in this establishment.
